page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the Java SDK'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first completions call with the Java SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free* The current version of the Java Development Kit (JDK)* The Gradle build tool, or another dependency manager.- An Azure OpenAI Service resource with the `gpt-35-turbo-instruct` model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.> [!div class="nextstepaction"]> I ran into an issue with the prerequisites.
